dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Wood County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Wood County, Wisconsin in 2020 and includes the layers 'Wood_Roads_2020' and 'Wood_ROW_2020'. [A line data-set that represents the Wood County road network. A single line is used to represent the center of a road. All roads are coded with an address range.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: [http://opendata.woodcogis.com/]
